    "headline": "MHS Launches Statewide Program to Help Indiana Medicaid Members with Employment",
    "summary": "Managed Health Services (MHS), a managed care entity and a company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), has announced the launch of the MHS Serves Workforce Support Program, a new statewide funding opportunity designed to strengthen workforce development programs that help Medicaid members prepare for employment, increase their income and build long-term economic stability. Applications are now open through June 19, 2026 and can be submitted through the MHS Serves online portal at mhsserves.org.",
